title: [Catacombs, Nexus]
description: All of the pipes seem to empty out into this general area, and large amounts of rancid water are unavoidable.

All of the pipes seem to empty out into this general area, and large amounts of rancid water are unavoidable.  Floating bones and refuse, among other debris, makes the water's level rise.  On the walls, mildew commemorates the different lines of water levels over the years past.
